@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
[*] --> Shipped
Shipped --> Archived : confirm
Archived --> OnHold : update
OnHold --> Draft : process
Draft --> Delivered : update
Draft : entry / log wishlist
Delivered --> Cancelled : review
Cancelled --> [*]
@enduml